Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 以世界为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 战斗 不停战斗的黑色勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于真正崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色勇者被守护世界的女神们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印在南端的遥远尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 那里还住着另一个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太过丑陋 无比孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独得快要死掉的寂寞恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此需要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能将你的身体给我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我吃掉你的半边身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是我的第一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你 我的身体根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.03,0:01:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个被称为「所有公式」的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便分成了「解开所有公式者」和「编造所有公式者」两部分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而勇者立刻吃掉了「编造所有公式者」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者将世界不断破坏 破坏 破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到达了其中心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而那里只有漆黑的绝望 痛楚 孤独 地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:57.20,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}追憶の扉を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:57.20,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}抬头仰望追忆之门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及黑暗 黑暗 黑暗 黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:03.20,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}聴いていた遠い囁き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:03.20,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}远处传来似曾相识的低语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:09.02,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}導いて魂の迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:09.02,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}指引我去往灵魂的迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想破坏整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:14.53,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}ひとひらの光の道へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:14.53,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}走上那一线光明之路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.30,0:02:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却要在这之前死去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来代替我承受这黑暗和痛楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:18.75,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}つらぬく痛みはInnocent Trick
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:18.75,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}痛彻心扉的是无辜的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用我剩下的身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:23.25,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}信じたいよ 孤独じゃないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:23.25,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}我相信自己并不孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将黑暗放进这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:28.62,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}此処は彷徨いのParadise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:28.62,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}此处是彷徨的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:34.56,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}白く心染める翼で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:34.56,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}展开将心染上纯白的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的恶魔 并没感到有多后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:41.30,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}もし君の瞳に 辿り着けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:41.30,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}若能映入你的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为即使只是一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只是一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为朋友而活过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:44.87,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}微笑って抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:44.87,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}请微笑着抱紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:50.70,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}生まれてきた意味を知る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:50.70,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}了解诞生的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的恶魔 是个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:58.69,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}見つめ合って創まるよ Destiny Regend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:58.69,ost2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}彼此凝望 去开创命运的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后 也是个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩那家伙好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人叫来自己却不在是怎么回事 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉乌前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们被叫来的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}远去时日的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 看起来像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你接下来打算把我怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早知道有一天会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:04:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要开始觉得事情会好转 可以一直持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就总是会突然变成这种局面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…想杀了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在你手下 或许也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能被你杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为啊 就算我这种人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也有个傻瓜会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经答应她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能杀我的人已经定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菲莉丝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先打破约定的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是把你当成挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你还是要杀我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定决定了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束一切吧 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还结束不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赢 上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求…雷鸣 电光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一切都是我下令研制的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这个国家干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 很普通的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只选择了一些必要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说因为必要就进行了人体实验？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底背负了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要一个人背负一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我帮不了你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你还把我当外人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是挚友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我啊 席恩·阿斯塔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鸣 电光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不会放弃的 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你牛角尖钻得多深
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么无可救药
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何陷入黑暗 无法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不会放弃你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你杀害同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起走吧 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在救出哭成这样的你之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的决定果然是正确的 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拯救你 无论世界变成怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的挚爱 寂寞的恶魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你 我才拔出了剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时间了吗 到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远 在永远的地狱徘徊的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要将你送去那里 送去 送去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁 α吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是α吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将化为「真」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不到时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点你也清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「编造所有公式者」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟然会做到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有点轻视你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快制止他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是很想吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在还不到时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键的他还是这种状态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样改变不了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救不了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括他 也包括你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还包括你最重视的那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你似乎还留有一点理智
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理智？你竟然会说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是想看看你身上的理智
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 席恩不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他绝不会失去理智
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我选择了他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他总是会选择正确的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩会背叛你 莱纳·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑陋的野兽 悲哀的恶魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前你就继续玩你的友情游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂他心中苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打着无聊的正义和爱的旗帜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一如既往地睡你的安稳觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂起床啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别睡啦 快起床 快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡糊涂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 让我帮你干活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己却先阵亡了 这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡着了吗 睡了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四小时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那些都是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其实 好像做了很…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的刚才我还记着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像是很令人不快的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:11:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还好我把你叫醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 帮大忙了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还说了什么「被熟女的胸罩包围我真是太幸福了」之类的梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还一直犹豫着要不要叫醒你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了 我的爱好泄底了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃不…你这么爽快就承认了 真是一点都不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就继续工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经做完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你给我上床好好睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你一个人把那些全解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛不叫醒我而自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 因为我叫你也不醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 啰嗦啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就别管了 快去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 睡了四小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以和你继续工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀 杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在此杀掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳就连死都死不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会永远…在地狱里徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我要 把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从黑暗里救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀不了这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有人赢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我们好脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是要前进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要将朋友当做祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打进地狱 再向前进？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可我是连杀莱纳…救莱纳都做不到的懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再苛责自己了 你的选择没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 你不必再苦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 接下来我会解决
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要继续
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人 这里禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 结果那小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没杀我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 看守大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想问你点事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在吗 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不在就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出一副那样的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…干什么？我还想问你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说…你真的死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…找了好久 一直在找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩说的话我也不信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在找 一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见过席恩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他变得好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑着说他杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得像要哭出来似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你不可能杀莱纳的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他 还是一直笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我不要再去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也别跟他扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他向奈尔法皇国出兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率领用禁忌之术创造的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:18:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将奈尔法人民全部杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全国人民都为他而狂热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说他是英雄王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要统治世界的英雄王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都疯了 大家都疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩 大家 整个国家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用再担心任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄王 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们逃了 追
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开了又怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去寻找 阻止他的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去揭开真相
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要平安逃掉啊 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着也跟死了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:36.73,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}忘れてたあの日の面影が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:36.73,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}那一天已忘却的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为自己是个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能留在人身边 也不能爱别人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:42.69,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}空の向こう 微かに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:42.69,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}在天空彼方隐隐浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就放弃了一切生存意义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:50.77,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}心なら繋がっていたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:50.77,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}心灵原本应早已相通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被你拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从心底被拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:58.25,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}震えた瞳は応えずに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:58.25,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}颤抖的瞳眸却无回应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可能看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:01.53,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}どんなに信じても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:01.53,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}如何相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:04.98,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}どんなに伝えたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:04.98,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}如何呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:11.28,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}この声は届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:11.28,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}这声音你已无法听到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求烧原·红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:16.07,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}光のフィルメント
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:16.07,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}光之Fillment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:20.93,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}全てをこの身体に刻み
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:20.93,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}一一铭刻于此身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃色的头发？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:26.04,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}歩き出す ここから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:26.04,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}就从此地 迈出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:29.72,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}記憶のセグメント
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:29.72,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}记忆的Segment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想回报你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:35.06,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}今絡まる運命の糸解き
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:35.06,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}解开此刻交缠的命运丝线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 现在虽然不知道你深陷什么困境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:38.94,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}強くなりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:38.94,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我会去到你身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:41.98,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}また出逢えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:41.98,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}若能再重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:51.55,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}もっと守れるように 君を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:51.55,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}定能守护你 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此不知道需要多大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但需要的我都会弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做好觉悟等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:12.12,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}解き放つたくさんの願いが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:12.12,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}被解放的众多心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你后悔那时没有杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:17.95,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}空の向こう 廣がる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:17.95,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}向着天空尽头蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到一个人擅自陷入绝望 背负一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要哭泣的你 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:26.45,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}心まで重なっていたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:26.45,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}连心灵都应早已相通
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承认你有一个最棒的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:33.49,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}震えた瞳が遠くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:33.49,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}颤抖的瞳眸却已远去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳 跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.80,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}どんなに失っても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.80,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}如何失去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也会前进的 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:40.16,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}どんなに通り過ぎても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:40.16,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}如何错过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:46.53,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}何度でも探すから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:46.53,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}多少次我都会去寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放弃你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:51.05,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}果てなきフィルメント
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:51.05,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}无尽的Fillment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:56.22,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}闇を切り裂く程の力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:56.22,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}足以划破黑暗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:22:01.40,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}手の中に摑んで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:22:01.40,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}我已握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:04.97,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}二人のセグメント
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:04.97,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}两人的Segment
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:10.30,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}もう誰かを傷付けたりせずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:10.30,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}已不想再伤害任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:14.06,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}生きて行きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:14.06,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}这样生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:19.35,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}前よりも真っ直ぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:19.35,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}想比以前更坦率地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:26.48,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}見つめたいから 君を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:26.48,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:22:53.49,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}もう一度 呼び合って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:22:53.49,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}再一次彼此呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.32,0:22:58.18,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}光のフィルメント
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.32,0:22:58.18,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}光之Fillment
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:23:03.22,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}全てをこの身體に刻み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:23:03.22,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}一一铭刻于此身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:08.33,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}步き出す ここから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:08.33,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}就从此地 迈出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:12.00,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}二人のセグメント
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:12.00,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}两人的Segment
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:17.46,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}今 どんな痛みも越えて行けば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:17.46,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}如今只要跨越所有痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.73,0:23:24.23,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}強くなれる また出逢えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.73,0:23:24.23,ost,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}{\blur6)}就能变得坚强 若能再重逢
